content: yungalgo: Merged 21 pull requests in `elizaos/eliza`, focusing on significant refactoring and bug fixes for the CLI and plugin system, totaling +10943/-7079 lines across 190 commits. Key contributions include resolving issues with CLI commands (`elizaos/eliza#4987`, `#4986`, `#4985`) and a major refactoring to centralize directory detection logic (`elizaos/eliza#5246`). They also implemented and later rolled back a change to the plugin architecture (`elizaos/eliza#5270`, `#5297`). Additionally, yungalgo was active in discussions, leaving 37 PR comments and conducting 4 code reviews.
